		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Im not sure if this will help, but here is an article covering some of the issues you stated:
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.vintagecomputing.com/index.php/archives/342">http://www.vintagecomputing.com/index.php/archives/342</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />It says a Genesis PSU will work fine if the polarity is rewired for the connector, since the voltage regulator is fine handling 9v.

		

